---
title: Mediterranean Pulled Pork Sub & Fries with Pear Salad & Truffle Mayo
description: Tired of eating shop-bought sandwiches? We know you are, so we’ve come up with a solution to rejuvenate your love for the sub by packing it full of succulent pulled pork in a tomato sauce that pop with juiciness. A helping of classic fries to dip in our truffle mayo and this is a sandwich you’ll never get bored of.
